WEBVTT

14:41.630 --> 14:44.800
"They that seek the Lord
shall not want for good."

16:52.636 --> 16:53.846
I need to close up.

16:56.598 --> 16:58.726
Do you answer your fucking phone?

17:00.853 --> 17:02.563
I was beginning to think you were dead.

17:02.646 --> 17:03.480
I'm closed.

17:03.564 --> 17:05.441
Get him out of here.

17:05.524 --> 17:06.442
Give us a minute.

17:08.444 --> 17:10.946
The boss is pissed...
he's been trying to reach you.

17:14.742 --> 17:17.077
You've been investigated
before... we all have.

17:19.913 --> 17:21.248
He's doing what he has to.

17:32.092 --> 17:33.594
What's the matter? Talk to me.

17:37.097 --> 17:38.682
I think I fucked up.

17:51.278 --> 17:52.696
What were you thinking?

26:18.076 --> 26:19.578
This is bullshit.

26:20.412 --> 26:21.496
This is serious.

26:21.580 --> 26:22.831
I'm trying to help you.

26:23.832 --> 26:25.584
By forcing me to make a statement?

26:26.126 --> 26:29.379
Without the American here,
just tell me what was on that tape.

26:31.965 --> 26:33.758
Just give me a goddamn statement.

26:34.301 --> 26:36.094
If you don't, you'll be suspended

26:36.177 --> 26:38.263
and go before the Security Council,
do you want that?

26:39.806 --> 26:41.057
You're threatening my job now?

26:42.100 --> 26:43.268
Take it however you like.

26:43.351 --> 26:45.895
I haven't done anything wrong.

26:45.979 --> 26:47.439
You erased an interrogation tape.

26:47.522 --> 26:50.442
I've erased a thousand tapes!
You know what goes on in there!

26:50.525 --> 26:53.820
-This is different!
-Because he escaped custody?

26:53.903 --> 26:56.573
No! Because it's on CNN.
The whole world is watching.

26:56.656 --> 26:59.326
It's not just your job. The Prime
Minister is on my back about this.

26:59.409 --> 27:00.493
Do you understand?

27:02.537 --> 27:03.496
Fuck this.

27:05.999 --> 27:07.459
Whatever you're hiding...

27:08.043 --> 27:09.544
I hope it's worth your career.

27:13.590 --> 27:14.591
Keys and ID.

27:27.562 --> 27:29.522
If I were you, I'd get an attorney.

41:55.262 --> 41:56.096
Jibril.

41:59.099 --> 42:00.559
Jibril, what happened to you?

42:01.268 --> 42:03.229
We've been looking for you for days...
